resolution.notes:
For the Guardian of Light Min Resolution is 1344x756.
If system setting "TV Resolution" is not 1080p, Dynamic Resolution range is 768x432-1280x720 for the Temple of Osiris, for the Guardian of Light it's 896x504-1280x720.

framerate.notes: In Temple of Osiris on top of API Lock there is Custom FPS Lock.
